CHARGING_STATUS , PMP_CHR_CHARGINGS.CHANNEL AS CHANNEL , PMP_CHR_CHARGINGS.LAST_TX_TIME_STAMP AS LAST_TX_TIME_STAMP FROM <?= odiRef.getObjectName("L", "PMP_CIS_CUSTOMERS", "EXTRACT_ORACLE", "D") ?>
